data.description: This house is ready to show   2 Hour notice to show/ see this nice property  Brand New Flooring and Counter tops !    The Master bath has an oversized jetted tub- beautiful.  Wood stove set up, just add the wood stove.  The roof is 7 years new    Seller is getting home ready to show so there are boxes in the garage  The garage is finished and the garage door is insulated. Plenty of room for your Horses or other animals and enjoy the land  Water system is owned and comes with the house The land has been cleared off by the Owner The flag pole does not stay. All the windows are triple pane you will notice how this home has no cold areas, it is well insulated and heated  The Sounds of Freedom as our Navy flies over your home !
